snippet.title: Cult of the Lamb - Pilgrim Pack Trailer | PS5 & PS4 Games
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/en-us/games/cult-of-the-lamb/

Join Jalala and Rinor as they journey across the Lands of the Old Faith, searching for a place to call home - as long as they can survive the dangerous Cultists looking for new sacrifices, the terrifying creatures hunting for a meal, and the strange mushroom-peddlars… not to mention rumors of a wicked beast who stalks the land, searching for their next victim…

This interactive adventure will show the world of Cult of the Lamb as you’ve never seen it before, with characters new and old to meet and mysteries to uncover.

The Pilgrim Pack releases on August 12!

#ps5 #ps5games #ps4 #ps4games #cultofthelamb
